---
import { literal } from "astro:schema";

const pageTitle = "关于我";

const identity = {
    firstName: "Kenga",
    country: "Chinese",
    occupation: "漂泊者",
    hobbies: ["读书", "倾听", "模仿"],
};

const skills = ["HTML", "CSS", "JavaScript", "C", "C++", "Java", "Python", "PHP", "Shell", "Astro", "Writing Docs", "AutoCAD", "SolidWorks", "Catia"
];

const happy = true;
const finished = false;
const goal = 3;
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{pageTitle}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">关于</a>
        <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
		<h1>我的 Astro 网站</h1>
		<h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
        <h2>...和我的新 Astro 网站！</h2>
        <p>我正在学习 Astro 的入门教程。这是我网站上第二个页面，也是我自己建立的第一个页面！</p>
        <p>随着我完成更多教程，该站点将更新，所以请继续查看我的旅程将如何进行吧！</p>
        <p>一下是关于我的几个事实：</p>
        <ul>
            <li>我的名字是{identity.firstName}.</li>
            <li>我住在{identity.country}。我的职业是{identity.occupation}。</li>
            {identity.hobbies.length >= 2 &&
                <li>我的两个习惯：{identity.hobbies[1]}和{identity.hobbies[2]}</li>
            }
        </ul>
        <p>我的技能是：</p>
        <ul>
            {skills.map((skill) => <li>{skill}</li>)}
        </ul>
        {happy && <p>我非常乐意学习 Astro!</p>}
        {finished && <p>我完成了这节教程！</p>}
        {goal === 3 ? <p>我的目标是在三天内完成</p> : <p>我的目标不是 3 天</p>}
	</body>
</html>
